y’s breathing, heart rate, and temperature, which can\nlead to death. Alcohol poisoning occurs when large quantities of alcohol\nare consumed in a short period of time, resulting in toxic levels of alcohol\nin the body.\nThere are many factors that can contribute to an unsafe blood alcohol\n• Speed of drinking\n• Full or empty stomach\n• Type of alcohol\n• The person’s weight and sex\nPoisons165",
