he skinPrevention\nTo reduce the risk of insect stings:\n• Wear a long-sleeved shirt, long pants, and closed-toe shoes.\n• Don’t wear perfume, cologne, or other products with strong scents.\n• Remove or cover items that will attract insects, such as garbage or\nWhat to Look For\nWhat to Do\nCall EMS/9-1-1 and get an AED if there are any signs of a severe allergic\nPoisons167",
